{"tid":1496221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嘅勇武派只係塞路掉石，真係好和平，好守禮。","createTime":"2019-08-22T11:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T17:15:49.000Z","uid":289775,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b56bac6d0635883516bc0a139aed1a8555e69023","tid":1496221,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EbhN1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EbhN1K.jpg&h=bd7a6a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼管轄的西巴布亞省今天爆發騷亂，數千名示威者縱火燒當地議會大樓，抗議印尼警方17日衝進大學宿舍，逮捕涉嫌毀損印尼國旗的43名滋事學生。<br />\n<br />\n印尼一有示威者被捕，就直接火燒重要建築物。<br />\n<br />\n香港人係學唔到印尼人，今次印尼發生騷亂嘅，係東部西巴布亞同巴布亞兩省，發動嘅全部係當地土著巴布亞人，同主導印尼政治及印尼最大族群爪哇族有極大文化差異，本身兩個省係印尼武力吞返嚟，加上長期歧視及冷落，好多巴布亞人都不滿印尼政府，獨立呼聲持續多年，佢哋有自組游擊隊同印尼軍警對戰，有槍有炸彈，實行武裝革命。<br />\n<br />\n而最近西巴布亞騷亂，某城市已經嚴重癱瘓，嗰啲示威者唔會同你講文明， 首先堵塞市內主要道路，然後四圍放火，將所有重要建築物燒晒，包括政府大樓，令市內大部分嘢停止運作，再衝入監獄放走囚犯，最後燒埋機場，由於示威者放火破壞係左一忽右一忽，市內警察都無符，全民皆兵，佢哋一早預咗攬炒，唔會主動同警察對碰，目標係破壞。<br />\n<br />\n5月份雅加達騷亂，有示威者只係帶毛巾包口，著拖鞋就出去同防暴隻揪，嗰啲示威者大部分窮到濃，反正乜都冇，就同你死過，好多人寫哂遺書準備死亡，郁起手癲過香港示威者好多，佢哋大部分人已經預咗冇命，所以最後死咗8個人。<br />\n<br />\n香港人？「我哋好文明」「唔好阻住我」「唔好搗亂」「你可以爭取，但係唔好影響到我」「你哋真係好自私，我要搵食㗎」「你收了多少錢」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有印尼朋友睇啲香港啲示威者同犬隻嘅衝突，直頭覺得香港啲示威者太淋，佢哋最鍾意四圍放火燒舖燒車，等啲警察心理上畏懼，汽油彈呢啲對佢哋嚟講好濕碎，但佢哋更鍾意用煙花同炮丈對付警察。但印尼警察都一樣係癲嘅， 射咗幾百粒催淚彈嗰啲示威者都唔肯走，就開真槍掃射，再出軍隊包夾。<br />\n<br />\n印尼朋友讚香港示威者好文明，同時又話香港示威者因為太規限於文明，所以永遠勇唔起。"},{"pid":"91ca1fb37d8db504a413b9df936333536ad132c3","tid":1496221,"uid":193237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"Dom生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfee1f32c96ca38910a9bea3bcfb8bbfb6396d0f","tid":1496221,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"墨西哥發生一宗警察強姦一名女子，上星期連續兩日爆發衝突，大批黑衫幪面 blackbloc既女示威者上街抗議及包圍放火魔法火燒警署。<br />\n<br />\n相反，將軍澳比人斬、阿伯醫院比警察虐待、新屋嶺警察私刑拷打，香港人都唔會上街放火魔法。<br />\n<br />\n香港人太多包袱？墨西哥人都有包袱㗎，唔好搵藉口啦！事實就係人地夠薑，香港人太怕事。睇返其他地方既遊行示威，每個人既面上都帶住憤怒，香港睇到既只係恐懼。要繼續行落去心態一定要變，就算唔走前線，都要有前線既憤怒，抗爭一定要每個人都懷住同一份為不公義而企出黎既心。<br />\n<br />\n係政權恐懼人民，唔係相反。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOPZ1n2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOPZ1n2.jpg&h=ac83a685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RYzQgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RYzQgq.jpg&h=b9c069df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ch4Wi9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fch4Wi9T.jpg&h=c95476ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ckf6Goe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkf6Goe.jpg&h=e15bb7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c8j1of.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c8j1of.jpg&h=626f2783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OyK3JBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyK3JBA.jpg&h=1340c1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfcHY9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfcHY9W.jpg&h=68c7bf03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOXps3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOXps3h.jpg&h=5c30a277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjAFLPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjAFLPY.jpg&h=a1844bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvME1oj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvME1oj.jpg&h=b9b825d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVprGok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVprGok.jpg&h=48d194f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PA7kLP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPA7kLP2.jpg&h=30d60bc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5c51c1a26f243e1efdd8aa9dda9d8df91a26552","tid":1496221,"uid":289775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyRd5Qg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyRd5Qg.jpg&h=fac17b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ghEWjah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FghEWjah.jpg&h=9fc82a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8oJBX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8oJBX.jpg&h=a9484915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYhAzJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYhAzJD.jpg&h=10051441&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4ff6c4e2653c3a155e235536391704da19292fa","tid":1496221,"uid":289775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"真係唔係鼓勵你哋衝，<br />\n不過政府港到香港市民好暴力， 暴動<br />\n<br />\n事實上香港嘅所謂暴動真係笑大外國人個口呀。<br />\n<br />\n若果真係暴動， 你估廣東道仲有玻璃係完整咩？<br />\n街上面嘅車輛仲有玻璃可以完好無缺？？<br />\n唔反車已經偷笑啦"},{"pid":"2132c181947c7d1ef64cf8ffb0db0c5c3b57b2d9","tid":1496221,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">８２３人鏈８２３人鏈８２３人鏈８２３人鏈８２３人鏈</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">８２３人鏈８２３人鏈８２３人鏈８２３人鏈８２３人鏈</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"33a6e2f25af0e331e2f371d54f46cc34e21e7072","tid":1496221,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"而家外國好多政客傳媒睇住香港<br />\n要佢地幫口俾壓力支那就唔可以超越底線<br />\n而家適量武力令狗出錯從而俾外國屌<br />\n起碼拖到人權法通過咁樣對我地更有利"},{"pid":"605b1d02acfef6ebfa5140f9037b15071273e1cc","tid":1496221,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p